data.description: A historic bungalow house that resides in a beautiful, quiet, country setting. This bungalow has great potential for renovation. for a majestic home. A two-bedroom, one bath, kitchen, dining room, enclosed porch, large utility room, oil heat/ wood stove, and base board heat hook ups. This home includes an attached one-bedroom apartment, with kitchen, stove, large living room, one full bath, closet and heat board hook ups. Great for guest. Also, this separate apartment has its own entry and driveway.   Detached garage behind house, that includes, work benches and wooded shelves. Wooded lot with four wheelers trails that leads to creeks. Also great for hunting.
